1. *Idiot* je vikao glasno. (The idiot was shouting loudly.)
2. On je obično *idiot*. (He is usually an idiot.)
3. Ona se ponaša kao *idiot*. (She is acting like an idiot.)
4. Ljudi su mu govorili da je *idiot*. (People were telling him that he was an idiot.)
5. Što si ti *idiot*? (What are you an idiot?)
6. Njegov brat je *idiot*. (His brother is an idiot.)